<COREF ID="34" TYPE="IDENT">It</COREF> 's the same sweet fragrance that fills the air everywhere you go when you 're in <COREF ID="43" TYPE="IDENT">Pinglin</COREF> .
<COREF ID="43" TYPE="IDENT">Pinglin Township</COREF> is situated in rural southern Taipei County .
Being relatively remote , <COREF ID="43" TYPE="IDENT">the area</COREF> was not developed until the late 18th century .
<COREF ID="43" TYPE="IDENT">Pinglin</COREF> is a pocket of level ground set in mountain forests , whence <COREF ID="43" TYPE="IDENT">its</COREF> name , which means " forest on level ground . "
