It seems just the way <COREF ID="43" TYPE="IDENT">it</COREF> was 20 - odd years ago , and gives the impression that in another 20 years time , <COREF ID="43" TYPE="IDENT">it</COREF> will still retain this way of life without the constant hankering for more .
