<TEXT PARTNO="003">
<COREF ID="40" TYPE="IDENT">Huang Kuei - ying</COREF> lives in <COREF ID="3" TYPE="IDENT">rural Pinglin</COREF> .
As a young girl <COREF ID="40" TYPE="IDENT">she</COREF> helped with the tea work , and later <COREF ID="40" TYPE="IDENT">her</COREF> husband also cultivated tea .
