<COREF ID="22" TYPE="IDENT">The proprietor , Mr. Chen ,</COREF> has been associated with tea since <COREF ID="22" TYPE="IDENT">he</COREF> was very young : " <COREF ID="22" TYPE="IDENT">I</COREF> never got very far in school , so the best thing is to keep on growing tea . "
