<TEXT PARTNO="004">
Tough times ahead for tea growers ?
The annual tea competition in <COREF ID="28" TYPE="IDENT">Pinglin</COREF> is a chance for <COREF ID="39" TYPE="IDENT">tea growers</COREF> to talk shop .
<COREF ID="39" TYPE="IDENT">They</COREF> examine and appraise the teas , note the aroma and the color of the steeped tea , and assess the good and bad points of every family 's tea .
