For better or worse , the tea growers ' reputations are made on such occasions .
According to <COREF ID="11" TYPE="IDENT">Mr. Chen</COREF> , <COREF ID="1" TYPE="IDENT">the growers</COREF> compare <COREF ID="1" TYPE="IDENT">themselves</COREF> with each other , discussing <COREF ID="1" TYPE="IDENT">their</COREF> processing methods .
