<TEXT PARTNO="005">
Hoping for fewer regulations
In early times <COREF ID="20" TYPE="IDENT">Pinglin</COREF> was a key waystation on <COREF ID="39" TYPE="IDENT">the Old Tan Lan Trail leading from Taipei to Ilan</COREF> .
These days <COREF ID="39" TYPE="IDENT">the old road</COREF> has been replaced by <COREF ID="41" TYPE="IDENT">the Taipei - Ilan Highway</COREF> .
<COREF ID="41" TYPE="IDENT">The current road</COREF> brings a lot of visitors to <COREF ID="20" TYPE="IDENT">Pinglin</COREF> and has made transport of the tea produce much easier .
