Many prized species of Taiwanese fish are being propagated .
In the pristine forests are ancient pine forests with species unique to <COREF ID="25" TYPE="IDENT">Taiwan</COREF> , and the deep blue skies attract waves of students to <COREF ID="20" TYPE="IDENT">Pinglin</COREF> to camp out and observe the stars .
